channel.title: RuneScape HiScore Grabber
channel.description:
Example: [url=http://www.installgentoo.net/%7Eaaron/rs_hiscore.php?user=username]http://www.installgentoo.net/~aaron/rs_hiscore.php?user=username[/url] (to update the info on the table use "&update=1" otherwise it wont update the info on the table) Source: [url=https://github.com/GXTX/RuneScape-HiScore-Grabber]https://github.com/GXTX/RuneScape-HiScore-Grabber[/url]
Keeps track of old info via MySQL and compares it with the recent HiScore info. The database structure is in the README file on GitHub.
This is released under the GNU GPLv2.
Enjoy.
